description: Not just another food truck. We serve high end restaurant quality food featuring wild game in tacos, sliders, salad wraps and sausages.  Created by world traveled classically trained chef of 40 years our menu changes to the season, event and best availability.  We also feature wild game but can completely change our menu to your event.  We also contribute 5% of our net profits to Homeless Veteran and Foster Kids organizations.
name: Fair Game the Nouveau Food Truck
